page.title: 11Housing
page.content:
Down at Donaldsons old timber yard,companies have{started building houses and other facilities.There are going to be approximately 47 private houses, approximately 68 private flats,special needs housing,a licensed restaurant, an old folks complex,21 industrial units and a chandlery and boat house.
Houses have been{built}along Queen street, called Servite houses, which were made for the old and the handicapped people.
There have been several{small {developments }in gap sights within the town and several older houses have been modernised or completely replaced by new houses.
